[quote]The basic thrust of the story is that the Nome King has captured and imprisoned several prominent citizens of Oz, including Ozma, Glenda, and Nick Chopper among others. He&amp;#039;s further gained control of the flying monkeys and, through them, Oz itself. The inhabitants of Wonderland are concerned, naturally enough, that he&amp;#039;ll soon see wage war against them as well. So the Cheshire Cat heads out in search of some new champions to help save those who&amp;#039;ve been captured and depose the Nome King.[/quote]

Captain Carrot And The Final Ark &lt;a href=&quot;
